{"word":"G3360 - μέχρι - méchri - mekh'-ree - Till","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μέχρι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">méchri</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mekh'-ree</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Till</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"வரைக்கும். மட்டும், பரியந்தம் - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"as far as, unto, until"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3372 - μῆκος - mēkos - may'-kos/3372\">G3372</a>; as <i>far as</i>, that is, <i>up to</i> a certain point (as preposition of extent [denoting the <i>terminus</i>, whereas <a href=\"#/G891 - ἄχρι - áchri - akh'-ree/891\">G891</a> refers especially to the <i>space</i> of time or place intervening] or conjugation): - till, (un-) to, until.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}